OL,5, Children of migrants who came to work  
OL,6, in Switzerland over decades are        
OL,7, demanding an apology for a policy they 
OL,8, say destroyed families and left many   
OL,9, traumatised.                           
OL,11,FFrom the 1950s right up until the      
OL,12,F1990s, hundreds of thousands of workers
OL,13,F- first from Italy, then from Spain,   
OL,14,FPortugal, and what was then Yugoslavia 
OL,15,F- made the journey to Switzerland.     
OL,17,FThey worked in factories, on roads and 
OL,18,Fbuilding sites, in restaurants and     
OL,19,Fhotels. Switzerland's highly successful
OL,20,Feconomy, its good infrastructure, is   
OL,21,Fwithout doubt due in part to them.     
